title: Season 4, Ep 33 - Cowboy World: Miss Quibbert Returns
description:
Arnie, Ulysses, and Champ get reacquainted with Miss Quibbert who arrives with some shocking news.


Credits

Arnie: Arnie Niekamp

Champ the Horse: Adal Rifai

Ulysses the Cowboy: Matt Young

Miss Quibbert: Sarah Shockey

Mysterious Man: Tim Sniffen
